/*
 * native_sim — simulation / development target
 *
 * No LoRa hardware overlay is needed: the gateway uses the LICHEN simulator
 * TCP driver (CONFIG_LORA_LICHEN_SIM) instead of a real radio when built for
 * native_sim.  The SLIP TAP interface provides host connectivity.
 *
 * The chosen zephyr,lora binding is intentionally omitted here; the simulator
 * driver registers itself at init time without a DTS node.
 */

